{"tid":883790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子自殺崖行山迷路 報警求救","createTime":"2018-10-31T05:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T05:46:12.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"11cdb9457a977e1a4f49dd795bdc6c137712ed6e","tid":883790,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"又一單迷路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正當救援人員在飛鵝山搜索懷疑迷路的行山女子同時，警方再接獲市民報案，在飛鵝山自殺崖迷路。上午11時左右，一名男子報警，表示行自殺崖路中迷路。警方、消防員、救護員到場搜索。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181031/58857685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181031%2F58857685&d=HetuhokjshoFeYmKQ5or8S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c84ef863\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181031%2F58857685&h=05910b8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181031/58857685</a>"}]}